    "script": "A: Did you hear what occurred at the market?\nB: Yes! A thief tried to steal from the gate.\nA: Who is in charge of the market?\nB: The manager. He contacted the police.\nA: Did they catch the thief?\nB: Yes! A customer helped locate him.\nA: That is amazing. The actual thief was someone we knew?\nB: Opposite to what we expected — it was a delivery worker.\nA: He used to deliver packages and earn trust.\nB: Exactly. He managed to steal several plates of gold.\nA: What reward did the customer receive?\nB: The market board gave him a set of gifts.\nA: That is the comfort of doing the right thing.\nB: True. Honest people always receive recognition.",
